drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"482a13026aa1cd851568e12b2fb03494f33ba95d","tid":1630664,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9370bfaf8505585e7592b3044cb62a3dd0734f4a","tid":1630664,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"鶳揸的士撞人，揸刀斬人嘅仆街冚家剷<br />\n打到人地成頭血做乜姐，佢幾日後就好返架啦，記者影到又咁肉酸<br />\n求下大家唔好再打到人爆哂血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係要照顧四肢關節呀</span><br />\n唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3505d0f1045d533f41daea909af779edbe06306d","tid":1630664,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15e6511d926d77ea9b6763e484fda37e9780d2b6","tid":1630664,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"古法炒麵: 鎚仔+厚書/木板？？"},{"pid":"91501326b946a333c031cb0c7a961d0901acc6d4","tid":1630664,"uid":128502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de2ea202c5956b224681dc4e3274aac6bf3034d3","tid":1630664,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"鐘意召喚獅鳥既後果只有一個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滿盤皆輸</span></span>"},{"pid":"894a2d1ed6aa9a8fc761b4340f7f22009e36f222","tid":1630664,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"前線真係要一人一本電話簿"},{"pid":"e7544b0cfe43324111587bc1a1cbf77a192622b8","tid":1630664,"uid":248932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9912c23c3594dba02cb0601f1d33cdfa22b29586","tid":16