r />\n還眼呀，2隻呀！！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"七隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4913c1da2ae1a0899c57977aee8a0885dd717ae","tid":1630664,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"[img]blob:<a href=\"https://web.telegram.org/178c1894-26b8-4706-8bdc-e349be81f1c8[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.telegram.org%2F178c1894-26b8-4706-8bdc-e349be81f1c8%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=6e13ee17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.telegram.org/178c1894-26b8-4706-8bdc-e349be81f1c8[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n#正確做法<br />\n【打斷藍屍手腳係為咗手足安全（二）】<br />\n今日有藍屍揸的士撞斷手足對腳，但藍屍只係受咗皮外傷，未做到斷手斷腳嘅效果。有位連登user嘅回應係「搵一個拉起隻手／腳，其他人踢踩 關節位 即斷」，呢個係正確做法，但大家可能會問實際即係點？<br />\n<br />\nHinge 嘅關節，好似手踭、膝、手指，本身結構係限死一個方向，而移動幅度係有限，咁執行公義嘅手足就可以反方向施力，就可以破壞關節。<br />\n<br />\n等第一波手足扑完藍屍／曱甴之後，等佢已經訓喺地下就可以落手。<br />\n<br />\n借鍳曱甴相同嘅制服方法，用膝跪喺目標人士嘅頸／膊頭上，然後落手，遇到嘅反抗會比較少。<br />\n<br />\n下列例子唔係要學啲咩花拳繡腿，只係需要睇個關節係點郁，而你用身體邊部份可以施力整斷佢。現場最好就係藍屍曱甴已經瞓喺地，然後一個手足抽起目標隻手／腳，另一個就用全身嘅重量／腳踢／踩。<br />\n<br />\n整斷關節示例<br />\n腕：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nwBFe6ZKAJs?t=500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnwBFe6ZKAJs%3Ft%3D500&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=0bb1d65f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nwBFe6ZKAJs?t=500</a><br />\n手踭：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nwBFe6ZKAJs?t=171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnwBFe6ZKAJs%3Ft%3D171&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=30857ad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nwBFe6ZKAJs?t=171</a><br />\n<br />\n至於左膠嘅問題，運動持續就快第四個月，面對左膠先警告後開拖係必須，唔好俾佢哋阻住你嘅逃生時間，左膠根本唔係自己人，向左膠執行公義嘅時候，諗一諗個女仔受過嘅傷：左腳開放性骨折、右膝頭甩骹，佢對腳將唔會百分百復元。<br />\n=====<br />\n重溫正論：<br />\n【打斷藍屍手腳係為咗手足安全】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual/22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual%2F22&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=c0e4f337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual/22</a><br />\n【散水論：你哋中晒計，留返下次智取】<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual/97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual%2F97&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6uSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=b2c39cf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual/97</a><br />\n=====<br />\n相關post：<br />\n[有圖] 傷者難以百分百復元，或有機會終身殘廢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631629/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631629/</a><br />\n私了嘅同我聽住，一撚定要斷手斷腳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629718</a><br />\n=====<br />\n請follow《香港革命指南》<br />\n@hkmanual"},{"pid":"5f1958d9d055816549e46220f382e4a8f54b4699","tid":1630664,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GTq3kV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GTq3kV.jpg&h=f0fc57dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eaf65a7151ddf0d6ec7007210aa421c67355e82","tid":1630664,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"形象工程日！！<br />\n<br />\n[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"}]}